FeedPackage.Description:
With service management library you can start and manage chains and contexts developed with Chains and communication services. Building up on the tcp protocol support, the "worker" and "admin" concepts are been introduced (admin as the manager process for multiple workers). All the possible actions between them are defined here, like starting, installing, uninstalling, versioning and general management. The responsible management component, the executioner, is also introduced. It is the part that starts modules using a given json configuration, coordinating admin, worker and update procedures.
